1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:06,840
Ijkuak ijkon yonochiu,

2
00:00:06,840 --> 00:00:12,700
Jesús oksejpa okinnotitij inomachtijkauan* ne itenko on mar itoka Tiberias.

3
00:00:12,700 --> 00:00:15,640
Ijkuakon ijkin okinnotitij.

4
00:00:15,640 --> 00:00:17,120
Simón Pedro,

5
00:00:17,120 --> 00:00:17,600
Tomás,

6
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:20,040
on yejuan kuitiayaj kouatsin*,

7
00:00:20,040 --> 00:00:23,080
Natanael yejuan chanej Caná de Galilea,

8
00:00:23,080 --> 00:00:24,660
Santiago niman Juan,

9
00:00:24,660 --> 00:00:26,260
ikoneuan Zebedeo,

10
00:00:26,260 --> 00:00:31,160
niman okse omemej inomachtijkauan* Jesús san sekan nemiyaj.

11
00:00:31,160 --> 00:00:32,840
Simón Pedro okinmijlij:

12
00:00:32,840 --> 00:00:35,040
—Nejua nonmichajsis.

13
00:00:35,040 --> 00:00:38,000
Yejuamej on oksekimej okijlijkej:

14
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:41,220
—Tejuamej no mouan tiaskej.

15
00:00:41,220 --> 00:00:45,800
Yejua ika oyajkej niman otlejkokej ipan sen barco.

16
00:00:45,800 --> 00:00:49,920
Pero ipan nochi on tlayoua xitlaj* michin okajsikej.

17
00:00:49,920 --> 00:00:52,640
Ijkuak ye uajtlanestiaya,

18
00:00:52,640 --> 00:00:54,720
Jesús nemiya itenko on mar,

19
00:00:54,720 --> 00:00:57,760
pero on nomachtijkej* xkimatiyaj ika yejua.

20
00:00:57,760 --> 00:01:01,000
Kemaj okomintsajtsilij niman okintlatoltij:

21
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:03,080
—Nokoneuan,

22
00:01:03,080 --> 00:01:04,520
¿xitlaj* michin nenkajsij?

23
00:01:04,520 --> 00:01:07,120
Niman yejuamej okijlijkej:

24
00:01:07,120 --> 00:01:08,480
—Ka,

25
00:01:08,480 --> 00:01:10,040
xitlaj tikajsij.

26
00:01:10,040 --> 00:01:12,420
Kemaj Jesús okinmijlij:

27
00:01:12,420 --> 00:01:18,840
—Xkonchapanikan nemomatlau iyekmakopa on barco niman nenkimajsiskej michimej.

28
00:01:18,840 --> 00:01:28,120
Ijki okichijkej niman kemaj xok ueliyaj kixtiayaj on inmatlau ne ijtik on atl pampa sanoyej* miyek michin ijtik uajlaya.

29
00:01:28,120 --> 00:01:32,840
Kemaj on nomachtijketl yejuan Jesús sanoyej kitlajsojtlaya*,

30
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:33,640
okijlij Pedro:

31
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:36,600
—¡Tlakaj yejua toTEKO!

32
00:01:36,600 --> 00:01:40,320
Niman ijkuak Simón Pedro okak ika yejua inTEKO,

33
00:01:40,320 --> 00:01:44,480
nimantsin onotlakentij pampa onotlakenkixtijka.

34
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:45,240
Kemaj,

35
00:01:45,240 --> 00:01:47,040
ijkuak yonotlakentij,

36
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:49,000
onatlajkal.

37
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:52,640
Niman on nomachtijkej* xuejka nemiyaj itenko on mar,

38
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:55,200
yej san kanaj cien metros.

39
00:01:55,200 --> 00:02:03,120
Yejua ika okuajuikakej on barco niman okuajteuilantiajkej on inmatlau yejuan tentiaya ikan michimej,

40
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:06,160
niman oajsikej itenko on atl.

41
00:02:06,160 --> 00:02:08,440
Ijkuak oajsikej ipan tlajli,

42
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:10,900
okitakej ye onkaj tlixochtli,

43
00:02:10,900 --> 00:02:13,280
niman ipan onkatka michin niman pan.

44
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:14,160
Jesús okinmijlij:

45
00:02:14,160 --> 00:02:20,680
—Xkinuajuikakan sekimej on michimej yejuan kemach onenkinmajsikej.

46
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:28,840
Simón Pedro otlejkok ipan on barco niman okitilantiaj on matlatl hasta atlatenko tentiaya ikan michimej uejueyimej.

47
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:33,240
Okajsikej michin se ciento uan tlajko ipan yeyi.

48
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:36,120
Niman maski sanoyej miyek katka,

49
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:38,240
on matlatl xotsayan.

50
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,600
Kemaj Jesús okinmijlij:

51
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:41,640
—Xuajlakan,

52
00:02:41,640 --> 00:02:43,240
xtlakuakij.

53
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:48,400
Niman nion semej de on nomachtijkej* xokinemilij kitlajtoltis akin yejua,

54
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:51,640
pampa kimatstikatkaj ika yejua inTEKO.

55
00:02:51,640 --> 00:02:54,020
Kemaj Jesús okinnisiuij,

56
00:02:54,020 --> 00:02:57,240
niman okontilan on pan niman okinmakak,

57
00:02:57,240 --> 00:03:00,800
niman sano ijki okichiu ikan on michin.

58
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:01,720
In yejua tej,

59
00:03:01,720 --> 00:03:11,000
ika yexpa okinnotitij Jesús on inomachtijkauan* ijkuak yoyoliu* niman yonoketsteu ipan itlalkon.

60
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,480
Ijkuak yotlakuajkej,

61
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:15,400
Jesús okitlajtoltij Simón Pedro:

62
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:16,440
—Simón,

63
00:03:16,440 --> 00:03:18,400
ikoneu Jonás,

64
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:21,280
¿más tinechtlajsojtla* xken yejuamej in?

65
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,720
Pedro okinankijlij:

66
00:03:22,720 --> 00:03:23,080
—Kemaj.

67
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:25,080
NoTEKO,

68
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:27,840
tejua tikmati ika nimitstlajsojtla.

69
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:29,120
Jesús okijlij:

70
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:32,760
—Tla ijkon xkintlakualti noborreguitos.

71
00:03:32,760 --> 00:03:35,720
Ika okpa oksejpa okitlajtoltij:

72
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:37,080
—Simón,

73
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:38,640
ikoneu Jonás,

74
00:03:38,640 --> 00:03:40,440
¿tinechtlajsojtla?

75
00:03:40,440 --> 00:03:41,800
Pedro okijnankijlij:

76
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:43,360
—Kemaj.

77
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,280
NoTEKO,

78
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:48,000
tejua tikmatstikaj ika nimitstlajsojtla.

79
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,180
Yejua okijlij:

80
00:03:49,180 --> 00:03:52,520
—Tla ijkon xkincuidaro noborregos.

81
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:54,960
Ika yexpa okitlajtoltij:

82
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:55,940
—Simón,

83
00:03:55,940 --> 00:03:57,600
ikoneu Jonás,

84
00:03:57,600 --> 00:03:59,040
¿tinechtlajsojtla?

85
00:03:59,040 --> 00:04:04,160
Pedro onajman pampa ika yexpa okitlajtoltij tla kitlajsojtla,

86
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:05,800
niman yejua okinankijlij:

87
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:06,960
—NoTEKO,

88
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:08,760
tejua nochi tikmati.

89
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:11,460
Tejua tikmatstikaj ika nimitstlajsojtla.

90
00:04:11,460 --> 00:04:13,120
Jesús okijlij:

91
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:16,120
—Tla ijkon xkintlakualti noborregos.

92
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:20,880
Ika tlen melauak nimitsijlia ika ijkuak más tikonetl katka,

93
00:04:20,880 --> 00:04:25,040
san tiuajmotlakentiaya niman tiaya kampaka tejua tiknekiya,

94
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:27,240
pero ijkuak ye tiueuentsin yes,

95
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:31,480
san tikinuajmelauas momauan niman okse mitstlakentis,

96
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:34,720
niman mitsuikas kampa xtiknekis tias.

97
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:37,280
Ijkuak Jesús ijkon okijtoj,

98
00:04:37,280 --> 00:04:42,320
okimachistij kenijki mikis Pedro niman ijki kueyilis Dios.

99
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:43,920
Kemaj okijlij:

100
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:46,120
—¡Xuajla nouan!

101
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:48,080
Kemaj Pedro ouajnokuep,

102
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:54,500
niman okitak ika kikuitlapanuiya on nomachtijketl yejuan Jesús sanoyej kitlajsojtlaya.

103
00:04:54,500 --> 00:04:59,720
(On nomachtijketl katka yejuan nemiya inakastlan Jesús ijkuak otlakuajkej,

104
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:02,040
niman ijkin okitlajtoltij:

105
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:03,160
“NoTEKO,

106
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:05,320
¿akinonon yejuan mitstemakas?”)

107
00:05:05,320 --> 00:05:07,780
Niman ijkuak Pedro okontak,

108
00:05:07,780 --> 00:05:10,160
ijkin okitlajtoltij Jesús:

109
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,680
—NoTEKO,

110
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:12,760
niman in uej,

111
00:05:12,760 --> 00:05:14,480
¿tlinon ipan nochiuas?

112
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:16,240
Jesús okijlij:

113
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:21,040
—Tla nejua nikneki para yejua ma nemi hasta ijkuak oksejpa niuajlas,

114
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:23,040
on xejua motekiu.

115
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:25,080
Tejua xuajla nouan.

116
00:05:25,080 --> 00:05:31,040
Yejua ika intech on nomachtijkej* opeu kiteneuaj ika on nomachtijketl xmikis.

117
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:34,200
Pero Jesús xokijlij ika yejua xmikis,

118
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:35,840
yej okijtoj:

119
00:05:35,840 --> 00:05:40,520
“Tla nejua nikneki para yejua nemis hasta ijkuak oksejpa niuajlas,

120
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:42,740
on xtejua motekiu.”

121
00:05:42,740 --> 00:05:48,240
In yejua nomachtijketl yejuan kitemachistia nochi ken okitak in tlajtlamach*,

122
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:52,400
niman okijkuiloj nochi in tlajtlamach* ipan in amamoxtli*.

123
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:55,600
Niman tikmatij ika on tlen kijtoua,

124
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,900
yejua tlen melauak.

125
00:05:56,900 --> 00:06:01,360
Niman no onkaj okseki miyek tlajtlamach* yejuan Jesús okichiu.

126
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:06,360
Niman niknemilia ika tla nijkuiloskia cada se de nochi on tlajtlamach*,

127
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:11,920
xonyaskia kanon kintlaliskiaj ipan in tlaltikpaktli nochi on amamoxtin.

128
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:18,680
Ma ijki nochiua.

